 <introduction>

<para><legacyBold>S#.Shell</legacyBold> - is a ready-made graphical framework with the ability to change quickly to your needs and with a fully open source code in C# language (enough basic knowledge).
</para>

<para>You don't need to waste time creating a GUI (Graphical User Interface), a ready-made robot is created faster without sacrificing application usability. Basic functionality for testing, trading, connecting to data sources, displaying charts, portfolios, positions, orders and trades is already in the box.</para>
<mediaLink>
<image placement="center" xlink:href="Shell_Title_00"/>
</mediaLink>

<para>The main features of the trading robot shell:</para>
<list class="ordered">
  <listItem><para>Full source code. Ideal for custom robots, or for your solutions.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para><legacyBold>Support for more than 70 connections</legacyBold> to various exchanges of the world 
<link xlink:href="ad178c36-15c8-4314-bc5c-56220f41a67e" />, 
<link xlink:href="b884020d-e4f0-4f7d-8de1-d75d052fe04b" />, 
<link xlink:href="4c2ed7ba-9cb8-45d4-90be-5dc79e7f13c9" />, 
<link xlink:href="b0198d6a-0667-45d4-b172-698afd3ca310" />.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Flexible user interface.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Testing strategies (statistics, equity, report).</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Save and restore strategy settings.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Simultaneous launch of strategies.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Detailed information about the strategy operation (orders, trades, position, profit, logs, etc.). Everything is clear and simple.</para></listItem>
  <listItem><para>Running strategies on schedule.</para></listItem>
</list>
